&gt; &gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt;&gt; - 204, 205, 206
&gt; &gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt;&gt; - 3xx redirection codes with stateful recoding of temp/perm
&gt; &gt; &gt;&gt; redirects.
&gt; &gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt;&gt; - 503 + retry-after info.
